A malicious payload from Email or USB:

User -> Email attachment / USB insertion -> Payload Detected -> 

Temporarily restrict User Access until endpoint is clean:
- From corporate resources
- On-premises apps
- SaaS apps
- Cloud Apps

-> Remediation
  - Automation
  - Security Analyst approval

-> Share Intelligence with Threat Intelligence -> Defender for Office ->
Remove Email attachments from companywide networks / Block it from future attacks ->

-> Access Restored.

